OL,3,CWoman guilty over crash which killed
OL,4,Cyoung parents
OL,6,FA woman has pleaded guilty to causing
OL,7,Fthe deaths of a couple in a crash
OL,8,Fwhich left their young son orphaned.
OL,10,FLaila Barnard-Wigley was in a black
OL,11,FMercedes GLA which collided with a red
OL,12,FPeugeot 2008 on the A165 at the
OL,13,Fjunction of Grindale Road in
OL,14,FBridlington on 7 May 2021.
OL,16,FDean Yarrow, 33, and his 32-year-old
OL,17,Fgirlfriend Faye Wardle, who were in
OL,18,Fthe Peugeot, died in the incident.
OL,19,FTheir two-year-old son was seriously
OL,20,Finjured but survived.
