OL,6,FBarnard-Wigley, 27, of Thorseby Avenue
OL,7,Fin Bridlington, was initially charged
OL,8,Fwith causing death by dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving but those charges were later
OL,10,Fdropped.
OL,12,FShe has now admitted two counts of
OL,13,Fcausing death by careless driving.
OL,15,FHumberside Police said she had been
OL,16,Fdriving irresponsibly on rural roads
OL,17,Faffected by heavy rain.
