OL,4,Cyoung parents
OL,6,FSgt Rob Mazingham, of the serious
OL,7,Fcollisions unit, said: "This was a
OL,8,Ftruly tragic incident that left a
OL,9,Flittle boy orphaned and devastated
OL,10,Ffamilies who continue to grieve and
OL,11,Fattempt to navigate a life without
OL,12,Ftheir loved ones.
OL,14,F"This has been an extremely complex,
OL,15,Fand lengthy investigation, and I would
OL,16,Flike to thank the families of the
OL,17,Fdeceased for their patience, and
OL,18,Fstrength throughout the entire process.
