OL,6,F"Every fatal collision we attend is a
OL,7,Ftragedy that didn't need to happen.
OL,8,FBehind every incident is a person,
OL,9,Fwhether that be someone's parent,
OL,10,Fpartner, child, sibling, or best
OL,11,Ffriend, and in almost every case it
OL,12,Fcould have been prevented."
OL,14,FBarnard-Wigley will be sentenced in
OL,15,FJanuary.
